WEBVTT


1
00:00:03.340 --> 00:00:05.340
Our Tokens set out through the Orphant Lands

2
00:00:05.340 --> 00:00:08.320
in search of a way to rebuild their lost civilization.

3
00:00:08.320 --> 00:00:10.320
Many dangers have beset them,

4
00:00:10.320 --> 00:00:12.320
and more still are to come.

5
00:00:15.700 --> 00:00:17.620
The search party never returned.

6
00:00:17.620 --> 00:00:21.540
The ones that remain have been overtaken by a sandstorm.

7
00:00:22.460 --> 00:00:24.580
Ahead, a great cave comes into view.

8
00:00:24.580 --> 00:00:26.500
A cave full of nothing but a shadow.

9
00:00:27.220 --> 00:00:31.320
[Sound of stones falling]

10
00:00:32.500 --> 00:00:35.080
[Muffled scream]

11
00:00:41.160 --> 00:00:42.420
Is everyone safe?

12
00:00:42.420 --> 00:00:43.460
There's a body next to me.

13
00:00:45.300 --> 00:00:46.740
We gotta get out of here.

14
00:00:46.740 --> 00:00:47.860
The tokens again flee.

15
00:00:47.860 --> 00:00:50.440
This time through the blanket of darkness ahead.

16
00:00:50.440 --> 00:00:51.220
I see the light!

17
00:00:51.620 --> 00:00:53.220
This time towards the light.

18
00:00:53.380 --> 00:00:55.800
The darkness has no sympathy for the lost,

19
00:00:55.800 --> 00:00:57.420
no respect for tradition.

20
00:00:57.460 --> 00:01:01.100
The remaining tokens leave their fallen where they lay.

21
00:01:02.760 --> 00:01:07.680
[Sound of water dripping]

22
00:01:10.760 --> 00:01:12.780
[Heavy breathing]

23
00:01:12.780 --> 00:01:13.780
Wait!

24
00:01:13.780 --> 00:01:15.640
Nao still lives.

25
00:01:15.640 --> 00:01:19.160
The crash of the cave was not enough to overcome his unending will.

26
00:01:19.740 --> 00:01:23.660
[Sound of footsteps]

27
00:01:23.660 --> 00:01:26.080
Oh, who’s there?

28
00:01:26.520 --> 00:01:31.280
Another useless Ethereum token trapped in the darkness away from his team.

29
00:01:31.400 --> 00:01:32.659
Who the hell are you?

30
00:01:33.480 --> 00:01:34.560
It doesn’t matter.

31
00:01:34.560 --> 00:01:37.960
Let’s say, I am ready to invest in your life.

32
00:01:38.120 --> 00:01:39.960
Life is the worst investment.

33
00:01:39.960 --> 00:01:40.600
[Troll-Hamster giggles]

34
00:01:41.060 --> 00:01:42.600
Don’t waste your time.

35
00:01:43.980 --> 00:01:45.980
You’d better find another ICO.

36
00:01:45.980 --> 00:01:48.980
It’s too dark here, and I’ve already found you, stupid.

37
00:01:49.120 --> 00:01:51.600
So, what do you want me to do?

38
00:01:51.600 --> 00:01:55.300
I want you to tell me why I should believe in you.

39
00:01:55.500 --> 00:01:57.140
Advertise yourself!

40
00:01:57.140 --> 00:01:58.620
Go and fuck yourself.

41
00:01:58.620 --> 00:02:01.200
[Nao coughing]

42
00:02:01.200 --> 00:02:03.200
I don’t need you to believe in me.

43
00:02:03.200 --> 00:02:05.200
Thousands of blocks ago

44
00:02:05.200 --> 00:02:08.820
we’ve started the fight with species like you.

45
00:02:08.820 --> 00:02:12.240
Greedy, stupid hamsters!

46
00:02:12.400 --> 00:02:16.460
You were obsessed with money and instant enrichment.

47
00:02:16.460 --> 00:02:18.040
Noooo...

48
00:02:18.040 --> 00:02:21.080
No... I will never let someone like you

49
00:02:21.080 --> 00:02:24.800
decide if I should live or die.

50
00:02:24.800 --> 00:02:26.800
[Troll-Hamster laughs]

51
00:02:26.800 --> 00:02:29.480
You are worth nothing, you little piece of shit.

52
00:02:29.480 --> 00:02:31.940
Your so-called life is just a lottery!

53
00:02:31.940 --> 00:02:34.760
I am Nao the Token.

54
00:02:35.700 --> 00:02:37.700
And I am not the lottery ticket.

55
00:02:37.700 --> 00:02:38.880
You are insane.

56
00:02:38.880 --> 00:02:42.660
I'm here in defiance of your tyranny.

57
00:02:42.660 --> 00:02:44.640
You want me to sell you my freedom?

58
00:02:44.660 --> 00:02:46.480
Not a big deal… But

59
00:02:46.480 --> 00:02:48.480
yes! I’m buying it!

60
00:02:48.480 --> 00:02:50.480
[Nao laughing]

61
00:02:50.480 --> 00:02:53.300
I like you. You are different.

62
00:02:53.300 --> 00:02:55.620
Too bad you are going die.

63
00:02:55.620 --> 00:03:00.100
It’s not you who is gonna decide this.

64
00:03:06.760 --> 00:03:11.300
Nao, bleeding a sea of red, has chosen freedom over Life.

65
00:03:11.300 --> 00:03:15.340
It will not be up to us whether he lives, or he dies.

66
00:03:15.340 --> 00:03:18.860
The Smart Contract of Deus ETH knows all.

67
00:03:20.060 --> 00:03:23.000
The Tokens’ journey continues in next week’s Episode,

68
00:03:23.000 --> 00:03:25.760
always for some, but never for all.

69
00:03:26.920 --> 00:03:30.640
Will your token survive?